name: HEALING GREEN IN MOTION
description: Healing Green was named after I made it because someone told me when they saw it reminded them of healing and related to the bible verse Rev. 22:2 and When I look at it, it makes me feel safe, peace, and faith. That day I realized my art can mean so much more than what I think and I love hearing other opinions! It fills my heart with joy, that I am able to relay messages with my art. Forever Grateful.Â
